title: Fashion Angels Fashion Design Sketch Portfolio
description:
Dream up and design your own fashion line with the Fashion Angels Fashion Design Sketch Portfolio.  Use the stencils to outline basic clothing shapes, then add your own details by coloring and embellishing with stickers.  Includes spiral bound portfolio book with 40 fashion sketch pages, 4 removable plastic stencil sheets, 1 sheet of stickers, and Instructional design guide.

Recommended Age: 6 yrs and up

10.5 in x 10.8 in x 0.5 in
